column3: For the years ended June 30, 2016 ("fiscal 2016"), June 30, 2015 ("fiscal 2015"), and June 30, 2014 ("fiscal 2014") Professional Employer Organization ("PEO") revenues are net of direct pass-through costs, primarily consisting of payroll wages and payroll taxes, of $30,928.6 million, $26,674.1 million, and $23,192.2 million, respectively.
